high_descs: Head to the passage on the right and walk to the kitchen on the right to face the cabinet on top of the cutting board.
Pick up a red onion on the left from the cabinet.
Turn around to face the sink.
Wash the onion in the sink and take it out.
Put the onion on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed onion on the left sink.

high_descs: Go towards the door to the right, then turn left and go into the kitchen area, turning right to the corner of the room with the cabinet.
Pick up the onion from the upper cabinet in the upper-right corner.
Go towards the sink behind you.
Wash the onion in the sink.
Place the onion on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash the onion with water and place it on the sink.

high_descs: Take the onion in the cabinet
Put the onion in the sink, clean it off
Place the onion on the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the onion in the cabinet clean the onion place the onion on the sink
